		<dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
			<deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromCutOffAndCompletenessPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">The data of copper slag treatment were mainly derived from a dominant copper company in China. The production data of cement and brick mostly came from real plant that adopts advanced equipment and processes, supplemented by published literature.</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">铜渣处理数据主要来源于国内某铜业龙头企业。水泥和砖的生产数据大部分来自采用先进设备和工艺的真实工厂，并辅以公开发表的文献。</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataTreatmentAndExtrapolationsPrinciples xml:lang="en">GaBi 4 software was used to model the copper recycling system and determine the environmental impacts in this study. The Eco-Indicator 99 (EI99) was applied for the life cycle impact assessment</dataTreatmentAndExtrapolationsPrinciples>
			<dataTreatmentAndExtrapolationsPrinciples xml:lang="zh">本研究中使用 GaBi 4 软件对铜回收系统进行建模并确定对环境的影响。采用生态指标99（EI99）进行生命周期影响评估</dataTreatmentAndExtrapolationsPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<referenceToDataSource type="source data set">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">Song, X. L., Yang, J. X., Wang, J. W. &amp; Wu, W. J. Assessing the Life Cycle Environmental and Economic Performance of Copper Slag Recycling. AMR 878, 219–225 (2014).</common:shortDescription>
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh">Song, X. L., Yang, J. X., Wang, J. W. &amp; Wu, W. J. Assessing the Life Cycle Environmental and Economic Performance of Copper Slag Recycling. AMR 878, 219–225 (2014).</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using the provided LCA data for recycled copper slag in cement and brick production, practitioners should apply the data corresponding to the specific recycling scenario relevant to their study. The use phase behavior and methodological considerations such as allocation procedures and the avoided burden method must be carefully followed as outlined by the Eco-Indicator 99 (EI99) approach. The functional unit for the assessment is 1 ton of recycled copper slag from the copper smelting process. Ensure compliance with the technological applicability relevant to the region's standards and practices.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用提供的铜渣回收到水泥和砖生产的生命周期评价（LCA）数据时，实践者应使用与其研究相关的特定回收方案的数据。必须仔细遵循使用阶段行为和方法学考虑，如分配程序和避免负担方法，正如生态指标99（EI99）方法所概述的那样。评估的功能单元是铜冶炼过程中回收的1吨铜渣。确保符合所在地区标准和实践的技术适用性。</useAdviceForDataSet>
		</dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativeness>
